title: Top Places to visit in Imphal West, Lamphelpat, Manipur
content:
Imphal West district is one of the sixteen districts of Manipur state in northeastern India. As of 2011 it is the most populous district in the state.
Lamphelpat is the district headquarters of Imphal West district in the state of Manipur, India. It is a suburb of Imphal city.
